Informing the app of your favourite Big Bash League outfit (international cricket is well catered for too) provides a bespoke guide to your team’s latest news, interviews, and a ball-by-ball service for all fixtures. It’s the perfect, easy-to-digest way to keep on top of your team’s movements—especially as passes can be purchased to enjoy live streams of matches.
